title.rendered: Havana Rattan 6 Seat Corner Set in Dove Grey

content.rendered:
The Havana rattan collection is an affordable solution for bringing your venue outside. The Havana range is made with a weatherproof rattan, ideal to be left outside. Woven with premium 15mm rattan and a metal frame.

The Havana Rattan 6 Seat Corner Set in Dove Grey comes with 2 three seater sofas, 1 coffee table and 1 tall side table.

This item requires self assembly.

12 month warranty. Furniture cover also available.

 As rattan is a hand-made item colours may vary on occasion, depending on the batch. Cushions are shower proof and must not be stored outside.
